{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"46fcde363e","title":"对中央警卫团一中队同志的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"17af539ab6","index":0,"year":1955,"month":7,"day":20,"articleId":"46fcde363e","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"指示","id":"2d13338754","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji35","name":"毛泽东全集第35卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/35-OCR.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]},{"id":"wansui3","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1949-1957卷）（1968年武汉版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui3a.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji35":{"comments":[{"id":"25aa686a24","publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"46fcde363e","publication":{},"article":{},"index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"1955年5月14日，毛泽东接见一中队的全体同志时，向他们提出学习文化的任务。中学课程一结束，根据毛泽东1957年的指示又办了业余大学。本篇一、二是毛泽东于1955年7月20日作出的具体指示。"}],"contents":[{"id":"669acc6eec","type":"title","text":"对中央警卫团一中队同志的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"46fcde363e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"25aa686a24","type":"paragraph","text":"根据你们的任务特点，可以少学点制式教练，多学一些文化科学知识，多学一些地理、历史、数学、物理、化学。五年中学毕业。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"46fcde363e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cf3dbdf2c8","type":"paragraph","text":"你们不要单武，而且还要成为有文化的政治人员。你们在这个学校学习七八年，就成了工农出身的大学生","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"46fcde363e","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":217,"end":217}},"wansui3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"bdd039e2d7","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五五年五月十四日，毛主席接见一中队的全体同志时，向大家提出学习文化的任务。今年七月二十日，又作了具体指示，他说：“根据你们的任务特点，可以少学点制式教练，多学一些文化科学知识，多学一些地理、历史、数学、物理、化学。五年中学毕业。”......中学课程一结束，根据毛主席一九五七年的指示，又办了业余大学。毛主席说：“你们不要单武，而且还要成为有文化的政治人员。你们在这个学校学习七、八年就成了工农出身的大学生。”","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"46fcde363e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d7e7aba2de","type":"title","text":"对中央警卫团一中队同志的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"46fcde363e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f33795bff1","type":"paragraph","text":"（摘自《中央警卫团一中队在职干部文化学习情况报告》）","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"46fcde363e","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":131,"end":130}}}},"__N_SSG":true}